{"tid":1403893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日下晝大約6點，海防道有架的士衝完路障夾硬衝向彌敦道人群","createTime":"2019-08-04T00:33:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T05:07:49.000Z","uid":245813,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9c93c842e8fb5d6a60dd6cade2544c9497222186","tid":1403893,"uid":245813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:33:15.000Z","msg":"當時我係真心行緊街<br />\n經過海防道行緊向海港城<br />\n當時海防道set咗roadblock，逼啲車唔好駛入彌敦道<br />\n點知有個的士阿伯夾硬撞開路障<br />\n周圍嘅人已經埋去喝住佢<br />\n跟住仲繼續衝向塞滿路人嘅彌敦道<br />\n群眾企喺車頭前面嘗試攔住佢<br />\n但的士佬竟然罔顧路面上嘅人嘅安全，死都唔停<br />\n場面非常危險<br />\n<br />\n當時應該有唔少人目擊到<br />\n現場亦都聽到有人話有記者拍低咗<br />\n亦應該拍低到車牌<br />\n呢啲危害市民安全嘅道路使用者一定要告到佢冇得再揸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0ccaf8e3a6db3d724ff85e879f515de1568f26","tid":1403893,"uid":245813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:38:18.000Z","msg":"有冇人記低咗車牌呀"},{"pid":"77359d786fce4118c5b5280933abe274419cf4e5","tid":1403893,"uid":245813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da8280a74e6ade9673d1da27fc8a4a8de085941","tid":1403893,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:17:22.000Z","msg":"hit and run"},{"pid":"6abb8102ceea594cd636675613fe13933aaf2ed8","tid":1403893,"uid":245813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:35:38.000Z","msg":"推到條揸車撞人嘅的士佬仆街"},{"pid":"98dc566a7774d21bebfd9e7777793ae14f018dca","tid":1403893,"uid":245813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6abb8102ceea594cd636675613fe13933aaf2ed8","tid":1403893,"uid":245813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:35:38.000Z","msg":"推到條揸車撞人嘅的士佬仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:42:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ef2e849fece8799f4dea6c403a7485ed4a2b5ee","tid":1403893,"u